source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_00<tab>Mimio would commend you for your accomplishments with the beast tribes, and entreat your further aid.
target: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_00<tab>不滅隊：作戦本部のミミオ少闘士は、蛮族5種族の信頼を勝ち取った冒険者に、折り入って頼みたいことがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_01<tab>Lieutenant Mimio Mio expresses her gratitude for your accomplishments, which have laid the groundwork upon which enduring peace with the beast tribes of Eorzea may one day be achieved. Valuing your diplomatic skills highly, she would seek your aid with an important task. Inquire with Lieutenant Gavin of Gridania's Order of the Twin Adder as to the details.
target: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_01<tab>ミミオ少闘士は、冒険者に特別な任務を頼みたいようだ。グリダニアの双蛇党：統合司令部にいる「ガヴィン少牙士」から詳細を聞こう。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_02<tab>Lieutenant Gavin is heartened by your presence, having heard of your peace-building exploits with the beast tribes. To learn more of the task the Twin Adder would entrust to you, speak with the lieutenant anew.
target: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_SEQ_02<tab>ガヴィン少牙士に声をかけた。任務の内容については、改めて説明するという。彼にもう一度声をかけ、任務について聞こう。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_TODO_00<tab>Speak with Gavin at the Adders' Nest in Gridania.
target: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_TODO_00<tab>双蛇党：統合司令部のガヴィン少牙士と話す

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_000<tab><var 08 E1E93501 ((<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>)) ((<var 08 E1E93601 ((<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>)) ((<var 2B ((<var 08 E1E93501 ((<var 28 ((GCRankLimsaMaleText)) E93509 /var>)) (()) /var><var 08 E1E93601 ((<var 28 ((GCRankGridaniaMaleText)) E93609 /var>)) (()) /var><var 08 E1E93701 ((<var 28 ((GCRankUldahMaleText)) E93709 /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>)) /var>)) /var>! Tales of your exploits with the lizardmen have been tearing through these halls like wildfire.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_000<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>殿。
キミの活躍は、不滅隊で語り草となっているよ！
蛮族問題を討伐ではなく、友愛と協調により解決するなんて！

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_001<tab>This realm has no dearth of adventurers capable of cutting down a beastman or two, but those with the aptitude and inclination to pave the road to peace are few and far between.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_001<tab>アマルジャ族のみならず、エオルゼアの主要蛮族である5種族と、
信頼関係を築いたそうじゃないか。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_002<tab>...And you have come at a most opportune time. The Order of the Twin Adder has need for an able ambassador, and I can think of none more suited to the task.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_002<tab>「武」とは戈を止むと書く……。
戦わずして平和を成す、これまさに「武」だね！
そんなキミに是非、お願いしたいことがあるんだ。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_003<tab>Our contact in Gridania is one Lieutenant Gavin. Seek him out at the Adders' Nest, and he will brief you on the particulars of the mission.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_003<tab>詳しくは、グリダニア「双蛇党：統合司令部」に務める、
「ガヴィン少牙士」から話を聞いてほしい。
よろしく頼んだよ！

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_004<tab>Our contact in Gridania is one Lieutenant Gavin. Seek him out at the Adders' Nest, and he will brief you on the particulars of the mission.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_MIMIO_000_004<tab>キミなら、必ずやこの任務を完遂できるはず！
詳しくは「ガヴィン少牙士」から話を聞いてほしい。
「双蛇党：統合司令部」に詰めている双蛇党党員だよ。

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_GAVIN_000_010<tab><var 08 E1E93501 ((<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>)) ((<var 08 E1E93601 ((<var 2B ((<var 08 E1E93501 ((<var 28 ((GCRankLimsaMaleText)) E93509 /var>)) (()) /var><var 08 E1E93601 ((<var 28 ((GCRankGridaniaMaleText)) E93609 /var>)) (()) /var><var 08 E1E93701 ((<var 28 ((GCRankUldahMaleText)) E93709 /var>)) (()) /var>)) /var> <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 03 /var>)) ((<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>)) /var>)) /var>! What I'd not give to hear of your adventures with the beastmen over a flagon of mead!
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_GAVIN_000_010<tab>おお、<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>殿か！？
双蛇党は今、貴公の話題で持ちきりなんだ。
是非今度、蛮族たちとの数々の冒険譚を聞かせてくれ！

source: TEXT_BANALL012_01467_GAVIN_000_011<tab>...And yet I fear that more pressing matters demand our attention today. When you are ready for your briefing, simply say the word.
target:
TEXT_BANALL012_01467_GAVIN_000_011<tab>……オホン、失礼した。
不滅隊のミミオ少闘士からの任務の件だな？
その件については、改めて説明させていただこう。
